{"tid":301558,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"憂中國票房數據造馬，荷里活製片商首度審計票房收入","createTime":"2017-06-28T17:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T05:34:04.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f917c757753b668b9634a28147bfacc05773cca","tid":301558,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:37:41.000Z","msg":"27/06/2017 15:18<br />\n<br />\n《經濟通通訊社２７日專訊》據外電引述知情人士指，荷里活電影製片商憂慮中國的票房數<br />\n據造假，首度委聘會計師事務所審計特定電影的票房收入。<br />\n　　報道指，是次審計由代表美國六家大型製片商的美國電影協會提出，料最快在第三季公布結<br />\n果。由於中國已有數百個虛報收入的事件，加上製片商在中國放映電影有收入分成協議，可獲票<br />\n房收入的２５％，準確的票房收入對華特迪士尼，及維亞康姆旗下的派拉蒙等荷里活主要製片商<br />\n尤其重要。<br />\n　　數據顯示，過去５年的中國票房收入的平均增速逾３５％，去年則放緩至不足３﹒７％，但<br />\n仍高於北美地區２％的票房收入增速。（ｋｌ）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN270627771&amp;page=1&amp;category=latest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fnewsid%3DETN270627771%26page%3D1%26category%3Dlatest&d=jzoBtcDn5a4I92ZefLOOqTM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=3eb41ef2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN270627771&amp;page=1&amp;category=latest</a>"},{"pid":"a98eb3ab95fc96cb63aa27ffe6516db62371555e","tid":301558,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T20:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0535dea7464dac1fe3d948bca5ab18b3dff282","tid":301558,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa532bdd5d1af489521c19a45a7d7ccad09ae4a","tid":301558,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:59:52.000Z","msg":"變窮金剛🙈🤦🏻&zwj;♂️<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid